des: Answer 5 random questions testing your knowledge of the episodes, gags, story lines, characters, songs and more from the popular TV show Bob's Burgers. With lots of questions to ensure that you can replay several times without repeats, the questions range from easy to challenging for those tried and true fans. Amaze your friends with your in-depth knowledge! Surprise your family with your Bob's Burger's wisdom! Astound your neighbors with your Bob's Burgers prowess!
